			Article        
		
| Management Science
		
		
		
		
		
		
		

How the Incumbent Can Win: Managing Technological Transitions in the Semiconductor Industry
Marco Iansiti
Keywords: Management; 
				  Technology; 
				  Transition; 
				  Semiconductor Industry; 
				  

